children.name: Rules
children.text:
This +1 Great Club allows the wielder to reroll 1's on damage rolls (second roll must be taken) and each time it hits a creature their speed is reduced by 5ft as they are slowly covered in slime. If this reduces their speed to 0 they become grappled in slime. 
The DC to escape is 12 and requires an action. This eliminates all previous speed reduction.
